(16, 'Icon Rocklear: Redefining Vehicle Protection - The Superior Alternative to Ceramic Coatings', '<p class=\"p1\">In the ever-evolving world of vehicle care and protection, a new champion has emerged, setting a higher standard in the industry: Icon Rocklear. This innovative product is not just another addition to the realm of car care; it is a groundbreaking leap forward, surpassing traditional ceramic coatings in both performance and durability.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>The Birth of a New Era in Coating Technology</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Developed with a blend of high-tensile materials from the Aviation, Automotive, and Marine industries, Icon Rocklear has been engineered to provide unmatched protection. Unlike standard ceramic coatings that have remained relatively unchanged since the early 2000s, Icon Rocklear represents a significant advancement, designed for superior protection, brilliance, and ease of cleaning.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Unrivaled Strength and Thickness</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">What sets Icon Rocklear apart is its extraordinary strength and thickness. Laboratory tests have proven that it is 75 times stronger than other coatings on the market. This robustness is complemented by a thickness that is 35 times greater than that of ceramic or graphene coatings. Such formidable properties ensure that your vehicle is shielded against the harshest elements and road conditions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Self-Healing and Durability</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">One of the most remarkable features of Icon Rocklear is its self-healing capability. Minor scratches and scuffs are no match for this coating, which boasts the ability to repair itself, maintaining a flawless finish. Moreover, its durability is unparalleled, with a guaranteed lifespan of 15 years under normal conditions, making it a long-term investment in your vehicle&rsquo;s protection and appearance.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Versatility and Ease of Maintenance</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Icon Rocklear is not just about robust protection; it\'s also about versatility and convenience. Its unique construction allows for the addition of wraps, vinyl, and paint protection film (PPF), without losing the benefits of the initial installation. Additionally, it requires zero maintenance, eliminating the need for frequent upkeep that is often associated with other types of coatings.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>The Sustainable Choice for Vehicle Protection</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">In today&rsquo;s world, where sustainability is increasingly important, Icon Rocklear stands out. Its long lifespan and renewability make it an environmentally friendly choice. The ability to reapply Icon Rocklear over itself without removing the basecoat establishes it as a sustainable, one-time investment for the life of your vehicle.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Conclusion: A Game-Changer in Automotive Protection</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Icon Rocklear is not just another coating but a system for life. Its unparalleled strength, thickness, self-healing properties, and ease of maintenance make it the superior choice for vehicle protection. Whether for a new car or a pre-owned unit, Icon Rocklear promises to maintain the brilliance and integrity of your vehicle\'s finish, far surpassing the capabilities of traditional ceramic coatings.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">For those looking to elevate their vehicle&rsquo;s protection to the next level, Icon Rocklear is the clear choice. It&rsquo;s more than a product; it\'s a commitment to preserving the beauty and longevity of your vehicle.</p>', 'Image-20240124-194259.png', 'Shawn S', '', '1', '2024-01-24 19:42:59', '2024-01-24 19:42:59', NULL),
